78
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,350
Tentu.

79
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:30,750
Hei, Lee Jung Joo!

80
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:33,510
- Ya?
- Ada apa denganmu?

81
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:40,080
Aku baru saja bertemu seseorang...

82
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:47,480
