00:18:59,230 --> 00:19:01,070
Ambil semuanya sebelum kau keluar.

233
00:19:06,690 --> 00:19:08,110
Tolong keluarlah!

234
00:19:41,130 --> 00:19:42,270
Apa kau baik-baik saja?

235
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:45,520
Ya

236
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:08,060
Kau melanggar tanah milik budaya, minum alkohol, dan membuang sampah...

237
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:09,440
Jadi kau akan dihukum.

238
00:20:11,300 --> 00:20:13,480
Ambil juga keresek hitam itu.

239
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:17,150
